              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A gas target, contained 99.4% deuterium. Three",
                "different gas targets were used, one for each of the",
                "angles investigated, the reaction products being",
                "simultaneously recorded by two cameras, one on each",
                "side of the target, with the exception of the 40",
                "degree target for which only one camera was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
